{"tid":2451103,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"哈利梅根名利雙收 加州大宅升值近3倍","createTime":"2021-03-18T00:55:34.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-18T08:43:05.000Z","uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"15a04164be4c4ee42504730a1ff6a8e1a6c8430c","tid":2451103,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T00:55:34.000Z","msg":"哈利梅根名利雙收 加州大宅升值近3倍<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://inews.hket.com/article/2902532/%E5%93%88%E5%88%A9%E6%A2%85%E6%A0%B9%E5%90%8D%E5%88%A9%E9%9B%99%E6%94%B6%20%E5%8A%A0%E5%B7%9E%E5%A4%A7%E5%AE%85%E5%8D%87%E5%80%BC%E8%BF%913%E5%80%8D\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2902532%2F%25E5%2593%2588%25E5%2588%25A9%25E6%25A2%2585%25E6%25A0%25B9%25E5%2590%258D%25E5%2588%25A9%25E9%259B%2599%25E6%2594%25B6%2520%25E5%258A%25A0%25E5%25B7%259E%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25AE%2585%25E5%258D%2587%25E5%2580%25BC%25E8%25BF%25913%25E5%2580%258D&d=1mBOIAkAA7%2FwaZBThmus2SL1bdbhbSvxCnYHZ8iA0HE%3D&h=5c3ec8f5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://inews.hket.com/article/2902532/%E5%93%88%E5%88%A9%E6%A2%85%E6%A0%B9%E5%90%8D%E5%88%A9%E9%9B%99%E6%94%B6%20%E5%8A%A0%E5%B7%9E%E5%A4%A7%E5%AE%85%E5%8D%87%E5%80%BC%E8%BF%913%E5%80%8D</a><br />\n<br />\n英國哈里王子與夫人梅根早前接受美國名嘴奧花雲費訪問，其訪問內容惹起社會各界熱議，令兩人瞬間成為全球焦點。哈里梅根的名氣大增，伴隨而來是利益收入。美國有當地地產經紀指出，哈里梅根在美國加州的豪宅比他們購買時升值近3倍。<br />\n<br />\n哈里與梅根在2020年6月斥資1465萬美元（約1.13億港元），在加州聖巴巴拉購入一間9間寢室和16間浴室的豪宅。豪宅位置優越，鄰近聖伊內斯山（Santa Ynez mountains）的登山徑，而且景觀極好，更附帶戲院﹑健身室﹑網球場及泳池等娛樂設施。<br />\n<br />\n當地的地產經紀表示，豪宅所在區域的售價起碼超過4000萬美元（約3.1億港元），比起哈利梅根當日的價格升近3倍。不過，有業者表明升幅並非與哈利梅根相關。"},{"pid":"830306d079b38d3cf8b329c8bf7a7a9613d59c48","tid":2451103,"uid":14918,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T00:59:27.000Z","msg":"億幾港紙有咁多野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n平過香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d125435d3dde083c994063e25b451fd833d6d970","tid":2451103,"uid":300782,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T00:59:28.000Z","msg":"想當年我仲讀緊BAND 3中學<br />\n<br />\n有條MK撚狗咁撚我, 話約我隻揪<br />\n佢以為自己有腹肌就好撚好打<br />\n<br />\n(但其實我當時己經舉左兩三年鐵,一直有飲奶粉<br />\n不過我BULK緊, 即係夜神起義 Bane 果種大隻型<br />\n所以D肌肉線條未現到出黎)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我D 毒撚FD 嚇撚到標尿<br />\n「唔好同佢打呀, 佢有腹肌架」<br />\n「你痴左線咩, 你見唔見到佢幾咁FIT 呀」<br />\n<br />\n我心諗話你怕你嬲<br />\n有腹肌唔等於有力量<br />\n我笑笑口咁答應左條MK 放學去籃球場打過<br />\n<br />\nfast forward 去到決戰時間<br />\n成班同學企哂係側邊睇<br />\n佢就除左件校服<br />\n成個小丑咁係到谷佢果幾舊腹肌仔 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n見到成班以為佢好好打果個情景,我真係快忍不住笑 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雖然最後佢打到我仆街, 牙都甩埋<br />\n但完全同腹肌冇關"},{"pid":"93329fd82d91095d82fbd29d0d898e98f0a6df5e","tid":2451103,"uid":18477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T01:01:54.000Z","msg":"113m喺香港都只係勉強夠買南區獨立屋<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4ad8cd52a00d77e5429cf8bd000048d7f7e89cf","tid":2451103,"uid":237581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d125435d3dde083c994063e25b451fd833d6d970","tid":2451103,"uid":300782,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T00:59:28.000Z","msg":"想當年我仲讀緊BAND 3中學<br />\n<br />\n有條MK撚狗咁撚我, 話約我隻揪<br />\n佢以為自己有腹肌就好撚好打<br />\n<br />\n(但其實我當時己經舉左兩三年鐵,一直有飲奶粉<br />\n不過我BULK緊, 即係夜神起義 Bane 果種大隻型<br />\n所以D肌肉線條未現到出黎)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我D 毒撚FD 嚇撚到標尿<br />\n「唔好同佢打呀, 佢有腹肌架」<br />\n「你痴左線咩, 你見唔見到佢幾咁FIT 呀」<br />\n<br />\n我心諗話你怕你嬲<br />\n有腹肌唔等於有力量<br />\n我笑笑口咁答應左條MK 放學去籃球場打過<br />\n<br />\nfast forward 去到決戰時間<br />\n成班同學企哂係側邊睇<br />\n佢就除左件校服<br />\n成個小丑咁係到谷佢果幾舊腹肌仔 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n見到成班以為佢好好打果個情景,我真係快忍不住笑 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雖然最後佢打到我仆街, 牙都甩埋<br />\n但完全同腹肌冇關"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T01:02:10.000Z","msg":"jm9"},{"pid":"8307fa0b9a266d080f7d900ccf5dd70f78bc5d74","tid":2451103,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T04:39:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e954aa55b16204c71d6e66bc86386eef34b3e5cb","tid":2451103,"uid":47475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"830306d079b38d3cf8b329c8bf7a7a9613d59c48","tid":2451103,"uid":14918,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T00:59:27.000Z","msg":"億幾港紙有咁多野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n平過香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T08:43:05.000Z","msg":"人哋啲豪宅係噉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HQJNTtwsEjs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DHQJNTtwsEjs&d=1mBOIAkAA7%2FwaZBThmus2SL1bdbhbSvxCnYHZ8iA0HE%3D&h=32a8c6ba\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HQJNTtwsEjs</a>"}]}